<h2>New Assignments from {{mentorName}}</h2>

<p>Hello {{menteeName}},</p>

<p>Your mentor has shared some follow-up assignments from your recent session. These action items will help you continue growing in your faith journey.</p>

<div class='info-box'>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Mentor:</strong> {{mentorName}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Session Date:</strong> {{sessionDate}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0;'><strong>Assignments:</strong> {{assignmentCount}}</p>
</div>

<h3>Your Assignments:</h3>

<div style='background-color: #F0F7F4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px;'>
  {{#each assignments}}
    <p style='margin: 0 0 15px 0; padding-left: 10px;'>
      <strong style='color: #3A5A40;'>{{inc @index}}.</strong> {{this}}
    </p>
  {{/each}}
</div>

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a href='{{appUrl}}' class='button'>View in App</a>
</p>

<p>Take your time working through these assignments, and don't hesitate to reach out to your mentor if you have any questions or need guidance.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  <strong>Tips for Success:</strong><br/>
  • Set aside dedicated time for each assignment<br/>
  • Take notes as you work through them<br/>
  • Discuss your insights in your next session<br/>
  • Reach out to your mentor if you need help
</p>

<p>Keep up the great work on your spiritual growth journey!</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  Blessings,<br/>
  <strong style='color: #3A5A40;'>The Spiriment Team</strong>
</p>
